///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//           ZenX PHP Data Manipulation Library README                       //
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

"zenx_etalon" folder contains master copy of all  library  files  required  for
development. 

If you only need to use the library you can download latest  release  from  the
project home page at 

											http://dk-lab.org/zenx.php



Basic library deployment is very  simple - just  copy  it  and  setup  database
access. For detailed instructions see 

			http://files.dk-lab.org/zenx/doc/ZenX/tutorial_Steps.pkg.html



"zxrelmkr.sh"  is  a  shell  script   generating   release   files  (separately
documentation and comments-stripped library package).
